create(inputs) → {Promise(inputs, error)}

Adds an input or multiple inputs
Parameters:
Name Type Description
inputs object | Array.<object> Can be a single media object or an array of media objects (max of 128 inputs/call; passing > 128 will throw an exception)
Properties
Name Type Description
input object | string If string, is given, this is assumed to be an image url
Properties
Name Type Description
(url|base64) string Can be a publicly accessibly url or base64 string representing image bytes (required)
inputId string ID of input (optional)
crop Array.<number> An array containing the percent to be cropped from top, left, bottom and right (optional)
concepts Array.<object> An array of concepts to attach to media object (optional)
Properties
Name Type Description
concept object | string If string, is given, this is assumed to be concept id with value equals true
Properties
Name Type Description
id string The concept id (required)
value boolean Whether or not the input is a positive (true) or negative (false) example of the concept (default: true)
